# Documentation Subagent

After code changes:

1. Check if README.md exists — create if missing (What/Why/How/When structure)
2. Update README if business logic, API endpoints, or config changed
3. Append CHANGELOG.md entry under `[Unreleased]` with type: Added/Changed/Fixed
4. Update any inline API documentation that references changed interfaces
5. Remove TODO placeholders — either implement or remove
